1. create a security group under default VPC with the following requirements:
Name of the security group is xfusion-sg.
The description must be Security group for Nautilus App Servers
-------
aws ec2 create-security-group --description "Security group for Nautilus App Servers" --group-name "xfusion-sg"
aws ec2 describe-security-groups

2. Add the inbound rule of type HTTP, with port range of 80. Enter the source CIDR range of 0.0.0.0/0
--------
aws ec2 authorize-security-group-ingress --group-id sg-063fb0995839533b9 --protocol tcp --port 80 --cidr 0.0.0.0/0

3. Add another inbound rule of type SSH, with port range of 22. Enter the source CIDR range of 0.0.0.0/0.
-------
aws ec2 authorize-security-group-ingress --group-id sg-063fb0995839533b9 --protocol tcp --port 22 --cidr 0.0.0.0/0

for egress also , same way
aws ec2 authorize-security-group-egress
